{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_22","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed for `dev.zio:zio-http_3:3.4.0`, but it did preserve a candidate branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-5178-fails-java-run-dev.zio-zio-http_3-3.4.0-b7a89e48\n\nMost likely, the run ended in the metadata/coverage verification stage rather than a remaining test failure. The initial JVM failure was in `Zio_http_3Test.urlsPathsAndQueryParamsRoundTripAndResolve()`:\n- `human-intervention-logs/dev.zio:zio-http_3:3.4.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-05T21-21-47-568868Z.log` shows `Expecting value to be false but was true` at `Zio_http_3Test.scala:92`.\n- `human-intervention-logs/dev.zio:zio-http_3:3.4.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-05T21-23-35-703209Z.log` and `.../gradle-test-2026-06-05T21-29-20-240958Z.log` then show the URL resolution assertion mismatch at `Zio_http_3Test.scala:115`.\n- However, later reruns passed in `human-intervention-logs/dev.zio:zio-http_3:3.4.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-05T21-29-53-587777Z.log`, `.../gradle-test-2026-06-05T21-31-44-540865Z.log`, and `.../gradle-test-2026-06-05T21-32-10-542376Z.log`.\n\nThe workflow still finished as failure because `generateMetadata` could not start the tracing agent: `human-intervention-logs/dev.zio:zio-http_3:3.4.0/native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-2026-06-05T21-30-41-917489Z.log` contains `Could not find agent library native-image-agent on the library path` and `libnative-image-agent.so: cannot open shared object file`. That also explains why dynamic-access coverage is unavailable and the metrics stayed `failure` after 3 iterations.\n\nSuggested next steps:\n1. Review the preserved branch and validate the candidate test/user-code-filter changes for `tests/src/dev.zio/zio-http_3/3.4.0`.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=dev.zio:zio-http_3:3.4.0` and `./gradlew nativeTest -Pcoordinates=dev.zio:zio-http_3:3.4.0` from that branch to confirm the candidate is still green.\n3. Fix the local GraalVM/native-image-agent setup, then re-run `./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=dev.zio:zio-http_3:3.4.0` so coverage can be collected and the run can complete."}}
